== 未來發展 ==
隨著士嘉堡輕鐵現有ICTS列車的車齡日增，TTC亦開始考慮車隊輪替的問題。現有的ICTS Mark I系列車已經停產，而TTC的選擇則包括從[[溫哥華架空列車|溫哥華架空列車]]購入二手Mark I列車、改建現有月台以迎合Mark II列車、或改用路面電車的車輛（即恢復當年的方案）。此外，當局亦曾數度考慮將[[布魯亞－丹佛線|布魯亞－丹佛線]]從堅尼地站伸延至士嘉堡來取代士嘉堡輕鐵，但地鐵列車不能安全地通過現有士嘉堡輕鐵走綫上的急彎，而另覓走綫則不合乎成本效益，因此布魯亞－丹佛線的延伸方案過去被認為是不可取。

及至21世紀初，士嘉堡輕鐵的去留仍未有定案。時任多倫多市長[[苗大衛|苗大衛]]曾於2009年聯同時任[[安大略省省長|安大略省省長]][[道爾頓·麥堅迪|麥堅迪]]宣佈撥款將士嘉堡輕鐵從ICTS系統改建為[[輕軌運輸|傳統輕鐵]]線<ref>{{cite web|title=Toronto's Transit City LRT Plan|url=http://transit.toronto.on.ca/streetcar/4121.shtml|publisher=Transit Toronto|date=2011-06-26|accessdate=2013-02-07|archive-date=2019-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812024232/http://transit.toronto.on.ca/streetcar/4121.shtml}}</ref>，並往東北伸延至[[百年理工學院|百年理工學院]]和雪柏大道東（{{lang|en|Sheppard Avenue East}}）<ref>{{cite web|title=Scarborough RT Route Diagram|url=http://www3.ttc.ca/PDF/About_the_TTC/Transit_City/SRT_route_diagram1.pdf|publisher=多倫多運輸局|accessdate=2013-02-07|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202512/http://www.ttc.ca/PDF/About_the_TTC/Transit_City/SRT_route_diagram1.pdf}}</ref>，但方案沒有落實。新任市長[[羅柏特·福特|福特]]則於2011年提出將[[艾靈頓輕鐵|艾靈頓輕鐵]]全線地下化<ref name="星島110401">{{cite news |work=《星島日報》加東版 |date=2011-04-01 |title=雪柏地鐵線延長 融資40億要商量 |url=http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/content_column_tor.php?IndexID=3102248 |accessdate=2012-11-30 |archive-date=2018-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180331040611/http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/content_column_tor.php?IndexID=3102248 }}</ref>，並將之與士嘉堡輕鐵合併，構成一條新的艾靈頓－士嘉堡線（{{lang|en|Eglinton-Scarborough Crosstown line}}），全線與其他交通分隔並以輕鐵車輛行駛，全長約{{convert|25|km|mi|1}}，造價約為82億元，當時定於2020年全線完工<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/toronto/torontos-eglinton-light-rail-line-to-be-funded-by-province-will-be-underground/article1964824/ |title=Deadlink |location=Toronto |work=The Globe and Mail |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110410114845/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/toronto/torontos-eglinton-light-rail-line-to-be-funded-by-province-will-be-underground/article1964824/ |archivedate=2011-04-10 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Eglinton light rail part of $12B Toronto transit plan |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/story/2011/03/30/transit-funding-eglinton.html |work=CBC News |publisher= |date=2011-03-30 |accessdate=2011-05-15 |archive-date=2012-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531001041/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/toronto/story/2011/03/30/transit-funding-eglinton.html }}</ref>。然而，該項方案不獲多倫多市議會接納<ref name="星島120209">{{cite news |work=《星島日報》加東版 |date=2012-02-09 |title=25：18票 市長福特地鐵夢碎 多市輕鐵方案去馬 |url=http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/content_column_tor.php?IndexID=3689055 |accessdate=2012-11-30 |archive-date=2013-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019074927/http://news.singtao.ca/toronto/content_column_tor.php?IndexID=3689055 }}</ref>。

市議會終在2013年10月以24票對20票通過將[[布魯亞－丹佛線|布魯亞－丹佛線]]伸延至士嘉堡中心，並於此後關閉士嘉堡輕鐵<ref name="Star20131008">{{cite web |title=Scarborough subway confirmed by Toronto council |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2013/10/08/scarborough_subway_confirmed_by_toronto_council.print.html |work=The Toronto Star |publisher=The Toronto Star |accessdate=October 8, 2013 |archive-date=2019-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812222011/https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2013/10/08/scarborough_subway_confirmed_by_toronto_council.print.html }}</ref>。延線包括三個新車站，項目造價約為35億6千萬元<ref>{{cite web |last1=Pagliaro |first1=Jennifer |title=Real costs of Scarborough subway, cancelled LRT to resurface at council |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2015/02/05/real-costs-of-scarborough-subway-cancelled-lrt-to-resurface-at-council.html |website=The Toronto Star |publisher=The Toronto Star |accessdate=July 24, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108092150/https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2015/02/05/real-costs-of-scarborough-subway-cancelled-lrt-to-resurface-at-council.html }}</ref>。市議會再於2017年3月通過延線採用麥高雲道（{{lang|en|McCowan Road}}）走線，並不於堅尼地站和[[士嘉堡中心站|士嘉堡中心站]]之間另設車站以減低項目造價<ref name="SSE Fast Facts">{{cite web |url=http://www.scarboroughsubwayextension.ca/fast-facts.html |publisher=多倫多市政府、TTC |title=Scarborough Subway Extension: Fast Facts |accessdate=2018-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180118161517/http://www.scarboroughsubwayextension.ca/fast-facts.html |archive-date=2018-01-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。延線全長{{convert|6.2|km}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ttc.ca/About_the_TTC/Projects/Scarborough_Subway_P/index.jsp |publisher=TTC |title=TTC Scarborough Subway Extension Project |accessdate=2018-01-24 |archive-date=2018-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180126004640/http://www.ttc.ca/About_the_TTC/Projects/Scarborough_Subway_P/index.jsp }}</ref>，具體造價尚未確定，但目前估計達33.5億加元<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2017/11/22/city-staff-say-updated-scarborough-subway-costs-wont-be-published-until-after-2018-election.html |title=Updated Scarborough subway costs won't be published until after 2018 election |newspaper=《[[多倫多星報|多倫多星報]]》 |date=2017-11-22 |accessdate=2018-01-24 |first=Jennifer |last=Pagliaro |archive-date=2018-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180125074607/https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2017/11/22/city-staff-say-updated-scarborough-subway-costs-wont-be-published-until-after-2018-election.html }}</ref>，暫定於2026年第二季開通<ref name="SSE Fast Facts"/>。

